videos.description: Isaiah Mobley puts his cape on and soars through the paint for the putback jam.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Isaiah Mobley put back dunk) 2022/03/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Mobley with the massive putback flush for USC

videos.description: Justin Kier pulls up and buries the 3-pointer from the top of the key for the Wildcats.
videos.headline: Kier pulls up and knocks down the 3 for Arizona

videos.description: Pelle Larsson lobs a beauty to Christian Koloko for the alley-oop to extend the Wildcats' lead.
videos.headline: Koloko throws down the hammer for an Arizona alley-oop

videos.description: Dalen Terry hauls in the dime from Azuolas Tubelis and lays it in for the Wildcats.
videos.headline: Tubelis with an absolute dime to Terry for the bucket

videos.description: Dalen Terry maneuvers through the Trojans defense and knocks down the basket.
videos.headline: Terry gets shifty and drains the bucket for Arizona

videos.description: Dalen Terry flies to the rim and throws down the half-court lob from Bennedict Mathurin.
videos.headline: Terry jumps out of the gym for this Arizona alley-oop

videos.description: Dalen Terry tracks down the ball and rocks the rim to extend the Wildcats' lead.
videos.headline: Terry hauls in rock and throws down the hammer for Arizona

videos.description: Justin Kier steals the rock and unloads a powerful jam for the Wildcats.
videos.headline: Kier gets it done on both ends of the floor for Arizona

videos.description: Oumar Ballo hauls in the elite dime from Bennedict Mathurin and flushes it home for the Wildcats.
videos.headline: Mathurin with the smooth no-look dime for an Arizona bucket

videos.description: Oumar Ballo snags the offensive board and puts it back for an Arizona and-1.
videos.headline: Ballo soars through the paint and drains the and-1
